    ai "공원에 가는 건 어때?"


# game/script.rpy:546
translate korean diner_f5bec36b:


    # jung "I'm cool with that."
    jung "좋아, 불만 없음."


# game/script.rpy:554
translate korean arcade2end_673eb881:


    # "She sees the poster on the wall about a firework display happening tonight."
    "그녀는 벽에 붙어있는 오늘 밤에 있을 불꽃놀이 포스터를 쳐다보았다."


# game/script.rpy:555
translate korean arcade2end_06513153:


    # ai "Hey!"
    ai "이것 좀 봐!"


# game/script.rpy:556
translate korean arcade2end_5ddea954:


    # "She looks at me pointing at the poster."
    "그녀의 눈동자는 포스터를 향해 있었다."


# game/script.rpy:557
translate korean arcade2end_78de6b21:


    # jung "I know. I see it."
    jung "알아. 나도 봤어."


# game/script.rpy:558
translate korean arcade2end_53763a45:


    # ai "Can we go?"
    ai "우리도 갈 수 있을까?"


# game/script.rpy:559
translate korean arcade2end_5c73cbc3:


    # jung "Sure. I also know a spot around there perfect for watching it."
    jung "물론이지, 거기에 나, 경관이 끝내주는 곳을 알아."


# game/script.rpy:560
translate korean arcade2end_23f0e11d:


    # ai "Really?"
    ai "정말?"


# game/script.rpy:561
translate korean arcade2end_e352569a:


