# game/script.rpy:580
translate korean hilltop_6541308a:


    # "I wish this could last forever."
    "이 순간이 영원하길."


# game/script.rpy:581
translate korean hilltop_34005493:


    # "But I'm running out of time."
    "그런데, 이제 가야 할 시간이네"


# game/script.rpy:584
translate korean hilltop_03c5cac4:


    # "She looks at me with a sad look."
    "그녀는 슬픈 표정으로 나를 바라보았다."


# game/script.rpy:585
