translate korean end_609a8922:


    # "It's an evaluation of a machine's ability to exhibit intelligence."
    "기계의 지능을 평가하기 위한 시험의 일종이지."


# game/script.rpy:600
translate korean end_eaf6ce0c:


    # "Whether it can act or speak like a human."
    "사람처럼 행동하고 말한다 해도,"


