    # "But however good a machine becomes..."
    "그렇다 해도, 아무리 성능 좋은 기계일지라도…"


# game/script.rpy:602
translate korean end_48c9a172:


    # "However indistinguishable it is from humans..."
    "사람과 구분 불가능하다 해도…"


# game/script.rpy:603
translate korean end_1f92ce69:


    # "It will never be an actual human being."
    "절대로 사람은 될 수 없다."


# game/script.rpy:605
translate korean end_82debffd:


    # "Just like Ai."
    "Ai처럼."


# game/script.rpy:606
translate korean end_5c8a2a86:


    # "No matter how good her program is."
    "그녀의 프로그램이 아무리 좋다 해도,"


